text:
="preserve">Sandra Sue Hutchens (March 18, 1955 – January 4, 2021) was an American law enforcement official and politician. She was the Sheriff-Coroner of Orange County, California from 2008 to 2019. Hutchens was born in Monterey Park, California.
Hutchens died on January 4, 2021 from breast cancer in Temecula, California, aged 65.
